[[File:Takeji kawamura.jpg|thumb|Kawamura Takeji]]

'''Kawamura Takeji''' ({{lang-ja|川村竹治}}) (September 1, 1871 – September 8, 1955) was a Japanese businessman and the 12th [[Governor-General of Taiwan]] (1928–1929). He was governor of [[Wakayama Prefecture]] (1911–1914), [[Kagawa Prefecture]] (1914–1915) and [[Aomori Prefecture]] (1917–1918).

